ing-relaxed text-[color:var(--color-diff-add-fg)]"><span class="block bg-[color:var(--color-diff-add-bg)]">+ Separate product decisions from implementation decisions.</span><span class="block bg-[color:var(--color-diff-add-bg)]">+ Identify whether each decision is reversible.</span><span class="block bg-[color:var(--color-diff-add-bg)]">+ Escalate unresolved product semantics before implementation.</span></pre><div class="flex gap-1.5 border-t border-border p-2 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider"><span class="rounded border border-foreground bg-foreground px-2.5 py-1 text-background">Accept</span><span class="rounded border border-border px-2.5 py-1 text-muted-foreground">Edit</span><span class="rounded border border-border px-2.5 py-1 text-muted-foreground">Reject</span></div></div><div class="mt-4 border-t border-border pt-3 font-mono text-[11px] text-muted-foreground">Nothing changes silently.</div></article><article class="flex flex-col rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-5"><div class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">03</span><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">Future work inherits it</h3></div><div class="flex-1 space-y-3"><div class="rounded-md border border-border bg-background p-3"><p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">You</p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-snug">Review the next design.</p></div><div class="rounded-md border border-foreground bg-foreground p-3 text-background"><p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-background/60">Airic</p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-snug">I found one irreversible product decision that needs your judgment.<br /><br />The remaining issues are implementation-level and can be revised safely.</p></div></div></article></div><p class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl text-center text-2xl font-medium leading-snug tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-3xl">Learning is not remembering what happened.<br /><span class="text-muted-foreground">It is changing what happens next.</span></p></div></section>
